{"id":296315,"type":4,"name":"Ruined King: A League of Legends Story","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b6/82/296315_8bb32.jpg","summary":"集结你的《英雄联盟》英雄小队，探索比尔吉沃特和暗影岛，解开致命黑雾的秘密。\r\n\r\n《破败王者：英雄联盟传奇™》是Riot Forge推出的首款基于《英雄联盟》宇宙的游戏。本作由Airship Syndicate工作室开发，其鲜明的美术风格出自传奇漫画家Joe Madureira（也是Battle Chasers和Darksiders两款游戏的制作人）。在这款沉浸式的回合制RPG中，你将控制一支由《英雄联盟》里的角色组成的队伍，自由配置阵容，探索比尔吉沃特的大街小巷、神秘的暗影岛，以及体验独特的兵线交战系统。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>破败王者：英雄联盟传奇</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/39135\">Airship Syndicate</a></li><li><span>发行: </span>Riot Forge (<a href=\"/person/35718\">Riot Games</a>)</li><li><span>别名: </span>聯盟外傳：殞落王者</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ルインドキング</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Ruined King</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox One</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS5</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox Series X/S</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>Turn-based RPG</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2021年</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://ruinedking.com/</li>","collection":{"wish":2},"crt":[{"id":2165,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/db/53/2165_crt_tdoqY.jpg","name":"阿狸","desc":"主角"},{"id":2232,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/83/ec/2232_crt_5kPc2.jpg","name":"布隆","desc":"主角"},{"id":51924,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/99/87/51924_crt_3g91J.jpg","name":"俄洛伊","desc":"主角"},{"id":52013,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/88/5e/52013_crt_cUzo8.jpg","name":"厄运小姐","desc":"主角"},{"id":86384,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c9/bf/86384_crt_86GEY.jpg","name":"亚索","desc":"主角"},{"id":86403,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/59/95/86403_crt_EGsY0.jpg","name":"派克","desc":"主角"}],"staff":[{"id":39135,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0e/7f/39135_prsn_Mj99V.jpg","name":"Airship Syndicate","desc":"开发